'''Ganner Squadron''' was a squadron temporarily established by [[Corran Horn/Legends|Corran Horn]] and [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] during the [[Second Galactic Civil War]]. It was named after fallen [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]], [[Ganner Rhysode]]. The squadron consisted of Horn, Antilles, [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Mara Jade Skywalker]].

